We're trying to save the
people we love right.

01:05:03.667 --> 01:05:05.002
- I never love this town.

01:05:06.770 --> 01:05:07.637
I always hated it.

01:05:07.637 --> 01:05:08.538
- Mike.

01:05:09.539 --> 01:05:11.275
- You're right, Carver.

01:05:11.275 --> 01:05:12.809
