01:09:48.184 --> 01:09:50.153
- Well, what about you?

01:09:50.153 --> 01:09:52.121
- Don't worry,
I'll be all right.

01:09:52.121 --> 01:09:53.323
- Okay, well, I'm not joking

01:09:53.323 --> 01:09:55.292
