01:11:22.546 --> 01:11:25.081
Listen, I really need the
keys to the mausoleum.

01:11:25.081 --> 01:11:27.216
Do you know where your
dad might have put them?

01:11:29.953 --> 01:11:32.356
Chad, listen, you're a
